				},
				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "When no valid companion for abduction is available, Orin insteadbducts Yenna -  a beggar child who previously greeted players when they entered Wyrm’s Crossing, and who subsequently keeps appearing in their camp. Appearing as Yenna, Orin will try to get the player to drink a poisoned soup, before revealing herself.\n\n\n\n She tells the player that the real Yenna is in the Bhaal Temple, and gives them an ultimatum about killing Gortash and retrieving the Netherstone. If they do this, then she will not kill Yenna, and will duel the player instead."
				}
			}
